y buildings.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-8-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-8-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-8-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575401\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575401\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-9-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern interior with dark cabinetry, a marble countertop, a glass decanter set on a tray, and sheer white curtains letting in natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-9-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-9-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-9-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575402\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575402\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-10-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with dark wood paneling, a concrete pillar, sheer curtains, black and white furniture, and a metallic ceiling fixture. Natural light fills the space.\" wid