h: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe materials are deliberately restrained – wood, concrete, natural stone, and brushed metal dominate – inviting attention to texture, craftsmanship, and the quality of light. Rather than overwhelming the senses, the design creates a serene backdrop where Shebib’s lifestyle, passions, and art can naturally unfold.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575404\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575404\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-12-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern interior hallway with a concrete pillar, large window, sheer curtains, wood flooring, and a framed poster on the wall; city buildings visible outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-12-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-12-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-12-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575405\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575405\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-13-810x1033.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with green vertical tiles, a matching countertop and sink, wall-mounted faucet, and a brown soap dispenser.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-13-810x1033.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-13-800x1020.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-13-768x979.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-13-1205x1536.jpg 1205w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575406\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575406\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-14-810x648.jpg\" alt=\"A narrow hallway with light wood floors leads to a small office area with shelves, books, and a desk under a window with natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"648\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-14-810x648.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-14-800x640.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-14-768x614.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575407\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575407\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-15-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern hallway with light wood flooring leads to a room with a piano; a built-in desk with shelves, chair, framed photos, and awards is visible on the right.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-15-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-15-800x1066.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-15-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-15-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBeyond its private areas, the penthouse also accommodates spaces for work, collaboration, and inspiration. Shebib’s personal atelier, designed for exploration and reflection, features a flexible Vitsoe 606 shelving system by Dieter Rams and a vintage Braun Audio 310 record player – nostalgic additions that nod to his late father’s stamp collection and enduring family connections.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575408\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575408\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-16-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Modern office with a desk and shelves on the left, a large concrete pillar near the center, and an open doorway revealing a bathroom with a lit mirror in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-16-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-16-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-16-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAn adjacent office space, intended for Shebib’s colleagues and collaborators, is furnished with a minimalist aluminum desk by Johan Viladrich and wire shelving by Belgian designers \u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/tag/Muller-van-Severen/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eMuller van Severen\u003c/a\u003e. Personal artifacts, including his Grammy awards and assorted keepsakes, are on display without taking over the space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575409\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575409\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-17-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern office with a red chair, metal desk, and grid-patterned shelves displaying books and awards, next to large windows overlooking greenery.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-17-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-17-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-17-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-17-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn the main suite, the sense of refined minimalism continues. A floating bed with an integrated desk, custom-designed by Reflect and fabricated by local artisan Mary Ratcliffe, seems to levitate within the room’s glass-wrapped enclosure. A Ceniza chair by EWE Studio and a whimsical pink Slide lamp by Sabine Marcelis add sculptural accents without disrupting the space’s tranquil atmosphere.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575410\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575410\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-18-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bedroom with a low dark wood bed, large sheer curtains, light wood floors, and a tall pink modern sculpture near a raised platform.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-18-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-18-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-18-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575411\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575411\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-19-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom with floor-to-ceiling window, cityscape view at dusk, sheer curtains, and a tall, pink LED floor lamp beside the bed.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-19-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-19-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-19-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575412\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575412\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-20-810x1013.jpg\" alt=\"A modern, minimalist bedroom with a geometric dark wood desk attached to the bed frame, paired with a matching chair, light wood floors, and sheer curtains in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1013\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-20-810x1013.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-20-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-20-768x960.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-20-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575413\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575413\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-21-810x970.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom with light wood flooring, beige built-in wardrobes, a black bed frame, and a geometric orange and blue wall art in the hallway.\" width=\"810\" height=\"970\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-21-810x970.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-21-800x958.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-21-768x920.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575414\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575414\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-22-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist living space with neutral tones, featuring a dark angular sofa, black chair, floor-to-ceiling windows with white curtains, and built-in storage cabinets.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-22-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-22-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-22-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMoving into the ensuite, a blue savoy stone bathtub commands attention with its dramatic veining, evoking imagery of cracking glaciers. The bathroom’s floor-to-ceiling glass shower, together with a sun collector–inspired vanity mirror, makes the most of the penthouse’s abundant natural light.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575415\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575415\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-23-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with grey marble surfaces, a white bathtub, double faucets, large angular mirrors, and a round ceiling light reflected above.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-23-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-23-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-23-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575416\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575416\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-24-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom interior featuring gray stone surfaces, a cylindrical concrete column, angular cabinetry, and large mirrored panels.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-24-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-24-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-24-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-24-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-24.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575417\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575417\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-25-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with dark stone walls, a built-in bench, a towel hanging on a black metal bar, and a tall, illuminated mirror.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-25-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-25-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-25-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-25-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-25.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOutside, the penthouse’s terrace has been entirely reimagined. Once a standard wrap-around balcony, it now boasts a reflecting pond, a lush garden, Italian-inspired alfresco dining, and a pool – all designed to offer moments of respite and reconnection with nature. These outdoor areas flow naturally from the interior spaces, blurring the line between indoor luxury and outdoor tranquility.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575418\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575418\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-26-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen and dining area with a large stainless steel island, minimalist furnishings, and floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking city buildings at dusk.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-26-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-26-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-26-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-26.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo support year-round comfort and energy efficiency, Reflect Architecture replaced the penthouse’s aging window walls with a high-performance glass system, minimizing thermal bridging while maximizing views and natural light. External shading devices were also installed to control solar gain and preserve privacy, making the home not just beautiful but also sustainable.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575419\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575419\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-27-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern rooftop patio with pink chairs and tables beside a pool, surrounded by city buildings and shade sails, at dusk.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-27-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-27-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-27-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Toronto-Penthouse-Suits-Reflect-Architecture-27.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on the 40 PH project or Reflect Architecture, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.reflectarchitecture.com/40ph\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003erefectarchitecture.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/2spacephoto/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eDoublespace Photography\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
